    This enumeration defines the possible prevent/protect statuses. This describes the current state of an incident in terms of how it has been remediated (in terms of either prevention - blocking an email for example, or protection - for example quarantining or changing access permissions on a sensitive document).

    The current prevent/protect status for an incident can be obtained from Incident.getPreventOrProtectStatus(). This can be useful to determine what steps to take to respond to the incident.

    A new value for the prevent/protect status can be set as part of returning a result from executing an action using ActionResultBuilder.setPreventOrProtectStatus(PreventOrProtectStatus).
